Package: valr
Type: Package
Title: Genome interval arithmetic in R
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Jay", "Hesselberth", email = "jay.hesselberth@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Jay Hesselberth <jay.hesselberth@gmail.com>
Description: Read and manipulate genome intervals and signals. valr 
             provides functionality similar to BEDtools and bedops within R,
             enabling facile interactive visualization of genome-scale data. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports:
    assertthat,
    dplyr,
    lazyeval,
    magrittr,
    purrr,
    readr,
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.2),
    stringr,
    tibble,
    tidyr,
Remotes:
    hadley/dplyr,
    eddelbuettel/BH
SystemRequirements: C++11
LinkingTo: Rcpp (>= 0.12.2), BH, dplyr
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat,
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
